Class FieldSetter<ft>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.FieldSetter<ft>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TextSetter

    public class FieldSetter<ft>
extends Object
    Reusable accessor object for setting a field in a tuple. Also manages reference-counting on the tuple.
